OL,4,Chit by car calls for safety
OL,5,Cimprovements
OL,7,FA woman from Oxfordshire who almost
OL,8,Flost her leg after being hit by a car
OL,9,Fis calling for safety improvements at
OL,10,Fa road crossing.
OL,12,FWendy Daniels was walking her dog when
OL,13,Fshe was involved in a collision with a
OL,14,Fcar at a pedestrian crossing on the
OL,15,FA40 in Eynsham last month.
OL,17,FShe said: "The next thing I remember
OL,18,Fis just a huge impact, absolutely huge
OL,19,Fimpact and just feeling a bit dazed
OL,20,Ftrying to reorientate myself.
