OL,5,Cimprovements
OL,7,F"It was very, very dark and I just
OL,8,Fremember thinking I am going to get
OL,9,Fhit again."
OL,11,FSurgeons managed to save her leg but
OL,12,Fshe now faces a long recovery.
OL,14,FMs Daniels wants to see improved
OL,15,Fsafety measures at the crossing and
OL,16,Fhopes her experience will encourage
OL,17,Fothers to wear visible colours and
OL,18,Ftake extra care at night.
