OL,7,FShe said: "If we're being signposted
OL,8,Fto use that as a crossing, then it
OL,9,Fneeds to be well lit.
OL,11,F"Drivers need to be alerted to slow
OL,12,Fdown."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Oxfordshire County
OL,15,FCouncil said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,16,Fthe victim of this incident.
