OL,7,F"We will work with our partners at
OL,8,FThames Valley Police, once they have
OL,9,Fcarried out any investigations, to see
OL,10,Fif there are any improvements that can
OL,11,Fbe made to increase safety.
OL,13,F"However, there are improvements
OL,14,Fplanned for the A40 in Eynsham as part
OL,15,Fof the A40 Eynsham Park and Ride to
OL,16,FWolvercote scheme, including upgraded
OL,17,Fwalking and cycling facilities,
OL,18,Fincluding new crossings and
OL,19,Fimprovements to existing ones."
